data.description: Discover serene living at its finest. Nestled in a peaceful, established neighborhood in Mapleton, you find this beautifully maintained 2-story home on over a third of an acre. This residence boasts both curb appeal and interior charm. From the grand entrance to the cozy living spaces, every corner of this home reflects a careful balance of style and functionality. The spacious yard is an oasis waiting to be explored, offering a lush canvas for gardening, outdoor gatherings, and endless recreational possibilities. The proximity to Hobble Creek Canyon, with all of its trails and adventures, along with several parks around beautiful Mapleton make this home one you will not want to miss!   Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from a previous appraisal.  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
